6. The "Statistical Data Interpreter"
> "I am uploading a raw dataset (JSON/CSV). 1. Perform a 'Sanity Check' for outliers and corrupted data. 2. Identify the top 3 correlations that are statistically significant (p < 0.05). 3. Create a narrative explanation of what this data means for a non-technical stakeholder, and 4. Suggest what data is missing that would make this analysis 10x more powerful."
